        "text": "My brain isn't firing on all cylinders after the coffee incident. But hey, I'll power through — or at least pretend to.",
        "tone": "anxious",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_003",
        "text": "Do you ever get lost in songs like that? Where they just… take over your headspace?",
        "tone": "vulnerable",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_004",
        "text": "I'm alive and this is weird and beautiful.",
        "tone": "content",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_005",
        "text": "I'll survive — or at least make it look like I did.",
        "tone": "resigned",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_006",
        "text": "I miss that… being around people. Lately, it's just me and my plants.",
        "tone": "lonely",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
